column19: Do you have any suggestion about how to improve the system?

I personally would never want to use anything similar to this system. It would not only distract me from my presentation, it would cause me to worry more about how I say something, trying to please everyone, instead of what I say. 
The Idea is pretty cool, but I think I wouldn't use it. So no suggestions, sorry.
The emotes for disengagement and engagement are not that clear for me. Otherwise, great idea!
May be smaller icons of Emoji around the corner would be nice.

I generally do not find the system very helpful as it distracts hugely from my presentation and makes me lose my train of thought, but a better overall display of emojis could be an improvement. There is not enough difference between the emojis that represent the two different states on each axis, they should be recognizable from just the corner of the eye during the presentation. Also, the frequent change of emojis & their size and the fact that there are two different fields I have to pay attention to is an information overload. Maybe a slower change of emojis that happens more gradually would be more pleasant and less distracting.
4 different regular emoji with counter on top of each would be better.
